      },
      "text": [
        " لُوطٍ ( عليه السلام ) هؤُلاءِ بَناتِي هُنَّ أَطْهَرُ لَكُمْ قَالَ عَرَضَ عَلَيْهِمُ التَّزْوِيجَ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from Muhammad Bin Abu Hamza, from Yaqoub Bin Shuayb, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> regarding the words of Lut<sup>as</sup> <span class=\"ibTxt\"><a href=\"/#/books/quran:11#h78\"><a href=\"/#/books/quran:11#h78\">[11:78]</a></a> These are my daughters (nation’s daughters)- they are purer for you</span>. He<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘He<sup>as</sup> presented to them for the marriage’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "7. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father from ibn abu ‘Umayr from Muhammad ibn abu Hamzah from Ya’qub bin Shu’ayb who has said the following: “About the words of Lot, ‘These are my daughters and they are cleaner and pure,’ <a href=\"/#/books/quran:11#h78\"><a href=\"/#/books/quran:11#h78\">[11:78]</a></a> abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘He offered them for marriage.’” "
        ]
      }
